package com.main

enum ShortDescription(shortDescription: String) {
  case Dragonborn extends ShortDescription("Dragonborn look very much like dragons standing erect in humanoid form, though they lack wings or a tail.")
  case Dwarf extends ShortDescription("Bold and hardy, dwarves are known as skilled warriors, miners, and workers of stone and metal.")
  case Elf extends ShortDescription("Elves are a magical people of otherworldly grace, living in the world but not entirely part of it.")
  case Gnome extends ShortDescription("A gnome's energy and enthusiasm for living shines through every inch of his or her tiny body.")
  case Halfelf extends ShortDescription("Half-elves combine what some say are the best qualities of their elf and human parents.")
  case Halfling extends ShortDescription("The diminutive halflings survive in a world full of larger creatures by avoiding notice or, barring that, avoiding offense.")
  case Halforc extends ShortDescription("Some half-orcs rise to become proud leaders of orc communities. Some venture into the world to prove their worth. Many of these become adventurers, achieving greatness for their mighty deeds.")
  case Human extends ShortDescription("Humans are the most adaptable and ambitious people among the common races. Whatever drives them, humans are the innovators, the achievers, and the pioneers of the worlds.")
  case Tiefling extends ShortDescription("To be greeted with stares and whispers, to suffer violence and insult on the street, to see mistrust and fear in every eye: this is the lot of the tiefling.")

}
